From 54b0b2b05ad4ceb5447b80653d933a5687fcfbe7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Rahman <danielsbhaucc@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 3 Jun 2026 20:27:02 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] refactor(notifications): response-based dormancy + remove
 dead engine

fetchTrueLastActiveByUser now counts only real responses (chat ai_interactions + task executions) with created_at floor; dropped middleware-bumped last_active_at so app-open no longer marks user active. Fix broken dormant phrasing and add dynamic-generation rule. Delete unwired /api/workflows/notifications engine (11 files); migration 000029 columns left dormant in DB.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
